body:
More food & tools adds over 275 new tools, foods, blocks, advancements, and ingredients to Minecraft.

This mod expands survival gameplay by introducing new crafting options using different materials, including emerald tools and multitools, as well as various food items such as sushi and other custom recipes.

Content includes:

New tools made from different materials;
New foods and ingredients;
New naturally generating plants;
New villager trades;
New advancements;
Simple **crafting**, and in **some functional blocks** recipes;
A lightweight gameplay expansion without complex mechanics;
Functional blocks;

The mod is designed to enhance survival gameplay and expand cooking options. It can be used in survival worlds or modpacks to add more content variety.

All content is created using MCreator 2026.1, texture maker: Iv411229 (planet minecraft)

Supported versions:
Minecraft: 1.21.8, 1.21.4, 1.21.1, 1.20.6
Loader: NeoForge

This isn't an addon for Farmer’s Delight — it's not recommended to use both mods at the same time.
Also, report about bugs or leave your ideas on planet minecraft (URL is report), I'm checking comments there almost every day a few times.
